{"tid":286220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Huawei 遇上「專利流氓」！被判敗訴旗下電話或被英國禁售","createTime":"2017-06-16T12:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T15:41:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33ae8614667340ea1fa9fcdc4bec58acf818112c","tid":286220,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"雖然透過申請專利各大小企業可以有效保障自己的技術，但有時它亦可能會被惡意利用。比如全球第三大生產商 Huawei，早幾年前就被一間名為 Unwired Planet 的「專利流氓」公司控告侵權。經過多年拉鋸後，近日英國高等法院終於判 Huawei 敗訴，除非他們為每部售出的機繳交專利費，否則其手機將可能會被英國禁售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解今次 Huawei 與 Unwired Planet 之間的官非已足足持續了三年有多，而經過今年 4 月裁決後，近日英國及威爾斯高等法院正式宣判 Huawei 侵犯了 Unwired Planet 所擁有的知識產權，當中絕大部份是 2013 年從 Ericsson 收購回來的 2,000 多項專利。留意在 4 月作出裁決後，Huawei 曾一度提出向對方支付專利費去庭外和解，但由於提出的時間太遲，因此 Unwired Planet 最後拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經裁決後法院宣判 Huawei 今後每售出一部機，都必須支付銷售價格的 0.032% 至 0.064% 作為專利費，而且不止英國出售的，就連全球售出的都要支付這筆費用，否則就需要在英國下架。據報以 Huawei 去年售出的數量來計算，需要繳交的專利費會多達 200 萬英鎊（約 1,991 萬港元）。Huawei 表示其業務不會受今次裁決影響，並會在本月底前提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n來源：The Telegraph<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=y8vGd2OV3ghg%2BXms0zhxk26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a0769ba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁 <a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=y8vGd2OV3ghg%2BXms0zhxk26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=36788eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a> <br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=y8vGd2OV3ghg%2BXms0zhxk26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=45ebb74e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"2628d1881fc7eb7084a121d1115c9959cb5c8231","tid":286220,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d104c0f7bc46043cdeb702ebe0be3cd05597b757","tid":286220,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"做乜唔上訴去樞密院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da106fadfb13fd7de48b58ef74efaf8ebcc1634","tid":286220,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ced8cf233c042688d353499ae0468faf955596d","tid":286220,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4400111085da6683b42d15605a8dbccc7a3a246","tid":286220,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321100ea2312eb956cf1f2ce20f327a097e93ad8","tid":286220,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n華為有專利但英國境內比第間公司霸左？<br />\n唔係既話人地明正言順有專利何來流氓<br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"8eeffa45ce01fd95bdffa0399372f7d8a6dd7a68","tid":286220,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"強國都蝦得人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835e4990de8f4d413c74b6bd0b75a2c3b63262fe","tid":286220,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"專利好似係分地域?"},{"pid":"34157e0e951f4a140903eab2a539684826dade16","tid":286220,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"裁決? 一張廢紙黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}